{"tid":1899264,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友有啲癖好搞到我都唔知點算好","createTime":"2020-02-26T13:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T00:21:51.000Z","uid":308964,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36f9bfe177c9a055a4fd823a70972dca49a8289a","tid":1899264,"uid":308964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"成日同男友道別果陣都會互相攬下<br />\n佢有時會摷吓我下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但咁都唔緊要<br />\n因為我都幾enjoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有時佢會摷埋我個袋袋<br />\n佢話我啲袋底泥好好聞 好頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到我有時都唔知比咩反應佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉<br />\n好能舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />救命<br />\n我就黎唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddeb9bc488215f9cff18f5597c65f4b7a5d4ee9","tid":1899264,"uid":218609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"幫你推下，見冇人覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bfbe7f17bb1ea021eb0ac8f3cf3b3284cac33e","tid":1899264,"uid":305971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2190ecd3f761ec16667e8f5e78b20ee63f82c2","tid":1899264,"uid":308964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":